        <section id="home">
            <h2>Home</h2>
            <p>The Royal Academy (TRA) is a co-educational, residential school with students from Grades 7 to 12. The objective of The Royal Academy is to stand out as a school of excellence, offering high-quality, wholistic education to its students, particularly those from the marginalised sections of society. The Royal Academy aims to create a student community that is balanced and diverse in terms of national character and cultural experience and has representation from all 20 Dzongkhags. As of 2025, The Royal Academy has a total of 334 students.

</p>
         <img src=https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/68b41787b0ee6a1df9470c7d/83a36f99-0034-4452-ae5b-4d6dd87b9311/IMG_0817.jpg" alt="students" style="width:900px;height:700px;">
