        <section id="Learning Experiences">
            <h2>Learning Experiences</h2>
            <p>1.Cross-Domain Learning : Students engage in learning that combines different fields such as Sports, Aesthetics, and Technology. This cross-pollination of ideas helps students gain a broader understanding of topics.
<br>

<br><br>


2.Extra curricular activities : Students participate in activities like sports, aesthetics, and have to take five areas of development as their domain enhancing creativity and fitness and not only that developing both emotionally and physically.
<br>
<br>
3. Learning Experience Outside Classroom: Opportunities for learning experiences oustside allow students to explore their interests deeply and gain a sense of connectedness with nature and beyond the classroom.
<br>
