        <section id="about me">
            <h2>About me</h2>
            <p>My name is Kinzang Choden, and I am currently studying in the ninth grade. I am from Mongar, a place that has played an important role in shaping my personality and values. In my family, I have three siblings including me, and I am the eldest one. Being the oldest has taught me responsibility, patience, and the importance of setting a good example for my younger siblings.

During my free time, I enjoy reading, writing, drawing, and painting. These hobbies allow me to express my creativity and explore new ideas. </p> 
